The '''Broer–Kaup [[equation]]s''' are a set of two coupled [[Nonlinear system|nonlinear]] [[partial differential equation]]s<ref>阎振亚著 《复杂非线性波的构造性理论及其应用》 第65页  科学出版社 2007年(in Chinese, SCIENCEP  2007)</ref>

: <math>u_{y,t}+(2 u u_x)_x + 2v_{xx} - u_{xxy}=0</math>
: <math>v_t + 2(vu)_x + v_{xx}=0</math>

